    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/db500175ec90b6b1d4a8b6ebc9a6c61c.poster.avif?t=1770948805\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/db500175ec90b6b1d4a8b6ebc9a6c61c.webm?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/db500175ec90b6b1d4a8b6ebc9a6c61c.mp4?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The killer is hiding among the passengers on the Fatal Train. <strong>Four detectives</strong> have taken on this challenging case. But honestly, does anyone care with everything else going on?<br><strong><span class=\"bb_strike\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/587d72c95574f3774559ec752744a701.poster.avif?t=1770948805\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/587d72c95574f3774559ec752744a701.webm?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/587d72c95574f3774559ec752744a701.mp4?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Would you like a cup of coffee, or perhaps you prefer whiskey? On this train, you’ll find exactly what you’re looking for: casinos, bars, a library, and even some old terminals. But wait... it seems one of the passengers is missing! Oh no he's dead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</span><br><strong>Detectives! let’s get to work!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/9b536c0f036950bd399cf4dea7554f7f.poster.avif?t=1770948805\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/9b536c0f036950bd399cf4dea7554f7f.webm?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/9b536c0f036950bd399cf4dea7554f7f.mp4?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><span class=\"bb_strike\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</span></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find out more about the passengers! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go through their belongings, open their briefcases, and watch their every move. Search the bodies for clues that might lead you to other, <strong>then let your revolver teach some manners!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/4ba90fd4950c23224291537e7097df8d.poster.avif?t=1770948805\" width=800 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/4ba90fd4950c23224291537e7097df8d.webm?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193920/extras/4ba90fd4950c23224291537e7097df8d.mp4?t=1770948805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_strike\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</span></strong><br>Good luck, detectives. The entire train is counting on you. And remember, at any moment, the train could catch fire, be struck by lightning, or be haunted by ghosts! But I have no doubt that our <strong>brave detectives</strong> will survive this crazy ride.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\"><strong>ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</strong></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Game in active development, wishlist and follow game to see more!</u></strong></p>",
